The pact monorepo contains both proprietary apps and open-source packages.

Apps under `apps/` are not licensed for redistribution.

Open-source packages under `packages/` are licensed individually:

- `@getpact/cli` - MIT
- `@getpact/verifier-sdk` (`packages/verifier-sdk-node`) - MIT
- `@getpact/adapter-sdk` - MIT
- `@getpact/adapter-slack` - MIT
- `@getpact/adapter-drive` - MIT
- `@getpact/adapter-partner` - MIT
- `getpact-verifier` (`packages/verifier-sdk-python`) - MIT

The MIT text for each open-source package lives at `packages/<name>/LICENSE`.
